Day22 of #24travelmoments : #Malacca, known as the "Historical state of Malaysia" and even one of the #UNESCO heritage, is one of the greatest attraction in Malaysia. Never did I know that I will set foot in the state of Malacca. Too bad we just stayed there for one afternoon. Would really love to stay and explore more of the Portuguese influenced state of Malacca. | August 2014 #24travelmoments @veerabianca
